(8230, '2007-11-02', 'Now On Steam - Sam & Max: The Complete Season One', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_1073\" style=\"display: ;\">
<p>The first season of Telltale Games\' flagship episodic series is now available in one delectable package. <a href=\"http://www.steampowered.com/v/index.php?area=package&amp;SubId=539\"><i>Sam &amp; Max: The Complete Season One</i></a> bundles the first six adventures of the dog-rabbity thingy detective duo at one terrific price. Buy before Friday, November 9, and you\'ll save an extra 10%!</p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
(8230, '2008-05-16', 'Sam & Max: Season 2 On Steam Now', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_1583\" style=\"display: ;\">
<p>Sam &amp; Max: Season 2, the latest in Telltale\'s flagship episodic series, is now available on Steam, a leading online platform for the distribution and management of PC games.<br/><br/>The complete Season 2 set is available for just $34.99, and the Season 1 and 2 complete sets are available in a collection for just $59.99. <br/><br/>To celebrate the launch of Season 2, all of Telltale\'s Sam &amp; Max episodes are available for 10% of their regular price during for the first week of Season 2\'s availability on Steam. <br/><br/>In other Steam news, Assassin\'s Creed is being offered for 20% off its regular price this weekend, and the following titles were added to Steamâ€™s growing library of PC games:<br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Iron Man (Sega)<br/><li>Soldier of Fortune: Payback (Activision)<br/><li>Monster Jam (Activision)<br/><li>History Channel: Battle for the Pacific (Activision)<br/><li>Cabela\'s Trophy Bucks (Activision)<br/></li></li></li></li></li></ul></p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>');
